## Unity Catalog Topology (per client)

```
{client}_raw   — extraction landing zone (bronze)
{client}_prod  — production dbt outputs (silver + gold)
{client}_ci    — ephemeral CI schemas: pr_{number} (auto-created/destroyed)
```

## Credentials

- All credentials in `~/.iron/env.local` — never commit secrets
- Key vars: `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`, `DATABRICKS_HOST`, `DATABRICKS_TOKEN`, `GITHUB_TOKEN`, `IRON_BUDGET_LIMIT`
- Local AI: `VLLM_BASE_URL` (localhost), `VLLM_BASE_URL_REMOTE` (Tailscale to Mac Studio)
